metadata.name: Magical Night 001
metadata.description:
Magical Night 001 is a piece from my digital paintings collection "The Shepherd series" which was by debut collection in the world of NFTs.

This piece is from the 3rd chapter of the series, previous chapters of 30 pieces were released on OS back in 2021.

The Shepherd is a series of hand drawn digital paintings about a Shepherd who is a traveler and an explorer. He is going on a very long journey to visit and experience new and surreal places.

Software: Adobe Photoshop CC 2018
Size: 8" x 10"
